query: SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating, MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor, MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, char_name AS chn, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, kind_type AS kt, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE kt.id = t.kind_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info not in ('book','LD laserdisc title','runtimes','tech info','production dates','LD quality program','goofs','weekend gross','LD frequency response','salary history','top 250 rank','LD pressing plant','other literature','opening weekend','LD original title','LD analog right') AND cct1.kind not in ('crew','cast','complete') AND chn.name not like '%Joker%' AND chn.name not like '%Gandalf%' AND chn.name not like '%Don Vito Corleone%' AND chn.name not like '%Captain Jack Sparrow%' AND chn.name not like '%Yoda%' AND n.gender not in ('f') AND mi_idx.info > '6.0'
